General.Name: Shelf Drilling (North Sea) Ltd.
General.Description: Shelf Drilling (North Sea), Ltd. operates as a shallow water offshore contractor in Southeast Asia, India, West Africa, North Sea, the Middle East, North Africa, and the Mediterranean. The company provides equipment and services for the drilling, completion, maintenance, and decommissioning of oil and natural gas wells and associated services. It owns and operates a fleet of independent-leg cantilever (ILC) jack-up rigs. Shelf Drilling (North Sea), Ltd. was incorporated in 2012 and is headquartered in Dubai, the United Arab Emirates.
General.Address: One JLT, Dubai, United Arab Emirates
